	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Centenę literę non sufficerent ad scribendas portentosas et inauditas rerum difficultates; sed simul presentia et abitus tabellarii non admisit plura.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sufficiat tibi hoc unum, quo insignis calamitas auguranda est, que nobis et vobis impendet.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Rex Gallię</persName> vel prorex contestabilis <persName type="auto_name">S. Quintinum</persName> novo presidio et commeatu munire voluit.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name">Regis Anglię</persName> exercitus hoc in tempore rescivit, abiturientes a Quintino vulneribus adfectos prostravit ita ut aliquot milia peditum et equitum <persName type="auto_name">Gallici</persName> exercitus sint extincta.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Contestabilis, comes a <placeName type="auto_name">Rheno</placeName>, <placeName type="auto_name">Rokgrad</placeName> et plerique ex maxima <placeName type="citizen_name">Gallicarum</placeName> familiarum nobilitate sint vel capti vel interempti.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tria millia peditum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Germanicorum</placeName> capta et ea lege dimissa, ut nunquam se sinant adversus <placeName type="citizen_name">Austriacam</placeName> domum conduci.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pfaffi erigunt cristas, non ideo quod <persName type="auto_name">Gallus</persName> evangelio faveat, sed quod fractis illius viribus <persName type="auto_name">Anglus</persName> commodius papatum defendere possit.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Polwilerus</persName> animosior factus sua aget; <placeName type="auto_name">Germania</placeName> sentiet denuo, quid sit futurm ex hac strage.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hac calamitate fiet, ut pleraque emergant clandestina facinora, que hactenus latuerunt abscondita.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nostra unica salus fuit ex hoc, quod Gallus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanos</placeName> et Hispani <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallos</placeName> a proposito retraxerunt.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ocyssime 20. augusti anno 57.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2856" cert="high">G[ereon]</persName> t[uus].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Equites, quos nigros vocant, sub <persName type="auto_name">Ernesto Brunsvicensi</persName> et <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18716">Ericho Brunsvicensi</persName> militantes potissimam huius victorię partem obtinent.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Hainricho Bullingero</persName>, viro doctissimo et pientissimo, domino et fratri charissimo.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Z(ü)rch.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
